snippet.title: GMOTA 1.3 trailer
snippet.description:
https://combine-kegan.itch.io/gmota

Want to help support further GMOTA development? Take a look at my patreon.
https://www.patreon.com/CombineKegan

The stalwart Kustam joins the fight in v1.3. Along with him comes a whole new mode in the form of Knightmare difficulty, featuring a revamped cast of monsters, along with a few other surprises.

Maps featured in the trailer:
-Castle Matias
-Bloody Graveyard
-Alfonzone
-Whitemare 2
-Whitemare 

an extra thank you to Skelegant, your constant help and support throughout this update has helped shape it into what it is now, I don't think I coulda done this without you.
